{
  "stem": "7832.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I don't think that half hour was a half hour.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was less than that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they marched us out of the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then they-- see, we lived on a-- on the street that led-- there was a T.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The main streets were a T-- one main street this way, and one this way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we lived on the T street.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we got to the corner of the other main street, we met with all the other people that were coming from the school.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the school was-- where they were confined-- was to our right, and-- to our left.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the railroad station was to our right.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we all met everybody on that corner.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were coming down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they attached us to that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we went-- all of us went to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they put us on this little train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But on the route, this was, like-- from the corner into the railroad station, maybe it's a half a mile.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But it was the longest half a mile in my life because so much bad things were happening on that half a mile.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All my friends that I was-- I went to school with, and I was so close with, and I shared things, and I even tried to celebrate Christmas with them, they were standing alongside of the road and yelling, oh, it's about time that you're going.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and we hate you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we don't want any Jews here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I could not believe what I was-- what I was seeing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that moment, I felt that-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there is just nothing for me, that wherever I'm going, there-- what is there?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My friends hate me.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
